{"tid":175593,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得「寧可信其有」係最垃圾最騎牆嘅句子？","createTime":"2017-03-27T14:54:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T10:39:17.000Z","uid":28031,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f46cac3d0356814bd3a2772efeccf1989ba18fc5","tid":175593,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T14:54:45.000Z","msg":"偏偏呢句野係大部分香港人（或華人？）嘅口頭禪<br />\n<br />\n我重記得細個見到家中長輩拜神，<br />\n我就問佢地，拜神佛真係有用咩？<br />\n「寧可信其有。」<br />\n<br />\n之後冇幾耐，佢地帶我去救世軍玩，<br />\n當時好似有啲基督教嘅活動，<br />\n我又問佢地，咁拜耶蘇又係咪真係有用架？<br />\n「寧可信其有。」<br />\n<br />\n到大個之後，每次無論上網定係現實有人討論鬼神宗教嘅話題嘅時候，永遠都會有人一句「寧可信其有」撻埋去。<br />\n<br />\n到今時今日嘅連登，<br />\n<br />\n上水炒車因爲果到好猛鬼？<br />\n「寧可信其有。」<br />\n 佛牌真係有用？<br />\n「寧可信其有。」<br />\n耶教？<br />\n「寧可信其有。」<br />\n我有陰陽眼，你問我答？<br />\n「寧可信其有。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每次見到呢句，你就可以醒覺，再講落去已經冇任何意思，因為佢地講得出呢句已經拒絕左正常思考，只係想明哲保身。<br />\n<br />\n得罪講句，呢啲人比奶共保平安嘅人更低賤。<br />\n<br />\n認同請正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd73ce3e4c284471b49447e8bbaf0680d5b351a7","tid":175593,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T14:56:44.000Z","msg":"呢句下聯係, 無成本, 點解唔做?"},{"pid":"25ab586f4cd843da68c01d865f8caf1b38a245eb","tid":175593,"uid":6352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T14:57:22.000Z","msg":"敬鬼神而遠之，信其有，係一種尊重。同時保持一定距離。"},{"pid":"73c22acd3d8940b0689a51d8f69cfb416130f072","tid":175593,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T14:57:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢句下聯係, 無成本, 點解唔做?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n事實係有成本，都有人仆倒去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n詳情請閲各大小宗教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d2221541fbd2ef9c85b45236b56ff470e18430","tid":175593,"uid":9136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T14:59:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢句下聯係, 無成本, 點解唔做?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n事實係有成本，都有人仆倒去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n詳情請閲各大小宗教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為人自卑, 覺得自己好多野都控制唔到, 咪幻想個神出黎拜以求安心"},{"pid":"060337cc150e27cad49e5e5ebc4568916bb44cdd","tid":175593,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T15:04:22.000Z","msg":"得罪講句，宗教係呢個世界上將呢句句子運用得最出神入化嘅表表者。<br />\n<br />\n當你抱住「寧可信其有」嘅心去信呢啲宗教嘅時候，其實代表你已經bam哂其他教派。<br />\n因為每個宗教之間都係互相矛盾緊，<br />\n而你又講到自己好開通，對所有宗教都「寧可信<br />\n其有」嘅時候，你已經落硬地獄了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （如有）"},{"pid":"104c6229be25cb8e0a80a45b64613302e59f9687","tid":175593,"uid":9681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T15:05:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得罪講句，宗教係呢個世界上將呢句句子運用得最出神入化嘅表表者。<br />\n<br />\n當你抱住「寧可信其有」嘅心去信呢啲宗教嘅時候，其實代表你已經bam哂其他教派。<br />\n因為每個宗教之間都係互相矛盾緊，<br />\n而你又講到自己好開通，對所有宗教都「寧可信<br />\n其有」嘅時候，你已經落硬地獄了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （如有）</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb676ec174a3d68f7c9e2b704a110d2235ee26ed","tid":175593,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T15:12:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>敬鬼神而遠之，信其有，係一種尊重。同時保持一定距離。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n風水 鬼神 宗教，永遠都有一班神棍係到搵緊食，<br />\n亦永遠有班人用你呢句説話幫佢地保駕護航，長撈長有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfa7540aee7d0490767d5879b4c37d322855fec8","tid":175593,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T15:12:54.000Z","msg":"大部份諺語都無經驗證<br />\n多數都係鳩嗡"},{"pid":"9258e8068aa91afa5cd0a9649dae7f4875d498e8","tid":175593,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T15:22:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大部份諺語都無經驗證<br />\n多數都係鳩嗡</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成日都話要是其是，非其非。<br />\n又話中立騎牆係幫凶，<br />\n偏偏去到呢啲話題就全部人婆仔上身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4e5d717a9f4885e778d1f0ac6560a5f1b4681e1","tid":175593,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T16:06:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efeeb93e285d72d7a2e595e96aed3f12e779fe24","tid":175593,"uid":80416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T16:16:38.000Z","msg":"呢句野意思係 信左又無蝕底既"},{"pid":"b715b993833aaf8b5916caac35823d1e227fa5e2","tid":175593,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T16:35:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢句野意思係 信左又無蝕底既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明明就係戴頭盔"},{"pid":"12241fc30c0d308545333f50ef9346c7a4921f93","tid":175593,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T23:32:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"556e520d1fafb089b371fe73338d50d371034286","tid":175593,"uid":98477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T00:02:33.000Z","msg":"巴打講得好。不論宗教，正信嘅教徒都唔應該迴避問題。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我有信仰都支持你咁講，因為寧可信其有唔係信仰，而係疑慮。"},{"pid":"f94040a1f7f82ad988b7c99546c1940393d6cba5","tid":175593,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T10:39:17.000Z","msg":"認真post冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}